<h3 id="staff-behaviour-change">Staff behaviour change</h3>

<p>We also provide our staff with regular reminders and tips on how to save energy in the office, such as:</p>

<ul>
  <li>turning off monitors when away from the desk</li>
  <li>greater use of video or telephone conferencing</li>
  <li>using the stairs instead of the lift</li>
  <li>displaying weekly energy use on news screens in the department</li>
</ul>

